title: SPY + COLE SEELY | A ROOKIE ON THE RISE
description: Amid a great rookie season, Cole Seely came out of the gate with a smile on his face and his sights set on the win. Combining raw talent with hard work, Cole currently sits in fourth place in Supercross points, and we're happy to watch his pursuit for the top step of the podium.
